{"tid":377581,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【原創MV】《新舊約》- 保育與發展之間","createTime":"2017-08-27T19:21:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-29T17:21:09.000Z","uid":43264,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2202fa895fb2f28c1507513386bd6d0ae6059b22","tid":377581,"uid":43264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T19:21:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=XmO5is5ZmD8&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DXmO5is5ZmD8%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=45QK8%2BHIcQDXOtE2NZYarf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=aeb22bff\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=XmO5is5ZmD8&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=XmO5is5ZmD8&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DXmO5is5ZmD8%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=45QK8%2BHIcQDXOtE2NZYarf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=aeb22bff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=XmO5is5ZmD8&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\n當我們越努力保護老去的；當我們越珍惜我們所擁有的；當我們明白興建很容易；當我們明白維繫卻很困難，誰還願意胡亂大興土木造成浪費？<br />\n<br />\n今天我們的世界正充斥著各種以「建設」為名的破壞，而真正的建設，只會建立在「愛護」和「珍惜」的基礎上。<br />\n<br />\n------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n《新舊約》<br />\n曲：林頌堯<br />\n詞：Rasaid Tsang<br />\n唱：梁浩森<br />\n<br />\n願   忘掉路邊的烙印<br />\n磨滅了   歲月裡的疤痕<br />\n淚   滲入腳下泥土栽種不幸<br />\n鮮花卻被折在瓦礫香消裡玉殞<br />\n<br />\n換上了   繽紛閃亮石頭<br />\n忘掉了   不新鮮的所有<br />\n誰願意   沙土沖刷過後<br />\n舊了當新   無論美醜<br />\n<br />\n若記憶   始終不敵潮流<br />\n如何才能珍惜這刻所有<br />\n曾綻放的煙花散去後<br />\n驟變污垢<br />\n<br />\n若   仍懷念街邊舊店<br />\n留住了   結局變得蕭條<br />\n月   往日結聚繁星天際閃耀<br />\n今天最耀眼是晚燈天空暗淡了<br />\n<br />\n換上了   繽紛閃亮石頭<br />\n忘掉了   不新鮮的所有<br />\n誰願意   沙土沖刷過後<br />\n舊了當新   無論美醜<br />\n<br />\n若記憶   始終不敵潮流<br />\n如何才能珍惜這刻所有<br />\n曾綻放的煙花散去後<br />\n驟變污垢<br />\n<br />\n是變遷   催趕生命運行<br />\n年月裡   雕刻多少足印<br />\n還是要   沖洗淹蓋變舊<br />\n又再嘆息   然後再生<br />\n<br />\n沒法可   貪新不念舊人<br />\n如何忘懷當天那點興奮<br />\n曾綻放的煙花散去後<br />\n別再吸引<br />\n<br />\n摘去了   鮮花丟在舊墳<br />\n泥下已   找不到的牽引<br />\n還是再   追憶都太過份<br />\n是要放手   還是抱緊<br />\n<br />\n舊了的   誰能隨意送贈<br />\n翻新的   再漂亮不過是為別人<br />\n忘掉了不會再吸引<br />\n<br />\n愛   殘舊了可會再吸引<br />\n<br />\n我   沉沒了不會再抖震"},{"pid":"27958695ba21c825536deb502987293c78ea11e1","tid":377581,"uid":43264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T02:48:53.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"efca8865f3dc4070e8d57c36155a9b9ab3bf8c06","tid":377581,"uid":43264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T08:02:34.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"db24de9801807fd40fe114a8a2cbc71e01cda7e3","tid":377581,"uid":43264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T10:39:09.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d29d267137807386c1664c20796d94b6e03f90f","tid":377581,"uid":43264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T19:51:06.000Z","msg":"Push!!"},{"pid":"b915bcc2aff4a84dfc7e52b8b6cec08d31084555","tid":377581,"uid":43264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T01:23:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7bd872b85e9761f3413fd2dfbe33a667c9825fe","tid":377581,"uid":93202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T02:36:31.000Z","msg":"支持下"},{"pid":"5decddd67579ff662acca07bf6b20a29b0c0b94f","tid":377581,"uid":43264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T17:21:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支持下</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝"}]}